abstract: >-
  JSON Schemas and Python contracts for AI agent memory integrity:
  evidence, candidate, ledger, taste, state, and ContextPack planes,
  with content-derived stable IDs and per-plane bundle validators.
  Standard-library only. Extracted from a 30+ sprint falsification-first
  AI agent memory kernel.
